These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
City: edinburgh, berlin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| City   | berlin    | edinburgh |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, analyst
1. the analyst is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the canadian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian  |
| Job     | analyst   | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, classical
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Music-Genre         | disco   | classical  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Cigar     | havana       | baccarat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, august
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Birthday        | february      | august  |
| Sport       | rugby     | cricket    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard |

