.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, singing
City: new-york, hannover
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | singing    |
| City   | hannover     | new-york      |
| Sport         | basketball | water-polo |

