.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
2 different games are played: chess, go
1. the person playing go is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Game   | go | chess    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |
| Flower        | begonia | azalea  |
| Sport       | surfing | volleyball |
| Transport   | bike    | helicopter |

