.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, march
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus  |
| Birthday   | march | april |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | lizard     |

